mum call stack size exceeded\"\",\"\"pid\"\":1,\"\"hostname\"\":\"\"currencyservice-2\"\",\"\"name\"\":\"\"currencyservice-server\"\",\"\"v\"\":1}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,currencyservice,currencyservice-2,\"{\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"time\"\":1750288733808,\"\"message\"\":\"\"conversion request failed: RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded\"\",\"\"pid\"\":1,\"\"hostname\"\":\"\"currencyservice-2\"\",\"\"name\"\":\"\"currencyservice-server\"\",\"\"v\"\":1}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,currencyservice,currencyservice-2,\"{\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"time\"\":1750289564739,\"\"message\"\":\"\"conversion request failed: RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded\"\",\"\"pid\"\":1,\"\"hostname\"\":\"\"currencyservice-2\"\",\"\"name\"\":\"\"currencyservice-server\"\",\"\"v\"\":1}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-2", "frontend-1", "currencyservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "currencyservice-1"], "service_name": ["frontend", "currencyservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-07"]}, "matched_anomaly": "The system experienced an anomaly from 2025-06-18T23:10:08Z to 2025-06-18T23:33:08Z. Please infer the possible cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-18 23:10:08+00:00 to 2025-06-18 23:33:08+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "metric_analysis_findings": "已成功收集到 UUID 为 `14c1047f-366` 的相关指标数据，并识别到了显著的异常指标，接下来将针对 Trace 数据进行分析。\n\n异常数据概述:\n- Time Range: 2025-06-18T23:10:08Z - 2025-06-18T23:33:08Z\n- 涉及的异常指标跨越多个服务，包括 `error_ratio`、`timeout` 和 `rrt` (响应时间)。\n\n我将继续对此数据进行全面的特征提取并列出分析结果。", "trace_analysis_findings": "以下是针对 UUID 为 **14c1047f-366** 所匹配到的异常调用链数据的初步分析结果：\n\n### 数据扫描发现\n\n#### **显著延迟调用链**\n根据异常时间段的调用链数据，对比正常和异常平均耗时，发现以下调用有显著的延迟倍数 (> 2.0 是显著延迟)：\n\n1. **CurrencyService/Convert**\n   - 正常平均耗时: 2350ms 到 2369ms\n   - 异常平均耗时: 9471ms 到 15499ms\n   - 异常倍数: **最高 6.57 倍（15499/2350）**\n   - 异常频次: **40 次**\n\n2. **CheckoutService/PlaceOrder**\n   - 正常平均耗时: 153703ms 到 156733ms\n   - 异常平均耗时: 51469392ms 到 1014008765ms\n   - 异常倍数: **最高 6464 倍（1014008765/156733）**\n   - 异常频次: **7 次**\n\n3. **CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies**\n   - 正常平均耗时: 2864ms 到 2962ms\n   - 异常平均耗时: 4798ms 到 5473ms\n   - 异常倍数: **最高 1.91 倍（5473/2864）**\n   - 异常频次: **14 次**\n\n#### **错误类型**\n检查状态组合数据，以下状态码和错误消息是异常的重要标志：\n\n- **HTTP status 500**\n  - 消息: \"failed to prepare order...\" 和 \"failed to convert...\"\n  - 异常频次多次出现在 **CheckoutService**\n\n- **context canceled**\n  - 出现在 CurrencyService 和 CheckoutService 调用链中\n\n- **connection refused**\n  - 错误: \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp... connect: connection refused\"\n  - 影响服务: CurrencyService 被 CheckoutService 和 Frontend 依赖触发\n\n- **transport is closing**\n  - 影响 CheckoutService 向 CurrencyService 的后续调用\n\n#### **拓扑关系中的异常传播**\n分析调用链上下游的波及影响：\n\n1. **Frontend -> Checkout**\n   - CheckouteService 的异常延迟显著 (1014008765ms)\n   - CheckoutService 同时传播 Context Cancel 或 Connection Error 到 CurrencyService\n\n2. **CurrencyService -> Backend**\n   - CurrencyService 的错误触发 `Connection Refused` 和 `Context Canceled`\n\n3. **RecommendationService -> ProductCatalog**\n   - **推荐服务**调用与 **产品目录**的延迟虽有异常但权重较小 (倍数未超过 2)\n\n---\n\n### 初步结论与假设\n根据上述异常链的扫描数据：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"checkoutservice->currencyservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"context_canceled\",\n    \"transport_closing\",\n    \"connection_refused\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"CurrencyService 调用扩展 Connection Refused 和 Context Cancel 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Context \\\"canceled\\\" 的错误频发于呼叫 currency 的链路。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Checkout 调用受 Currency 超慢响应延迟影响。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CurrencyService 的正常/异常耗时差距较大，超过正常耗时的 6464 倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Front-End 调用因上下游传播造成高延迟\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend 和下一个直接依赖链路的各服务耗时依次异常递增\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "我已经成功获取了 UUID 为 `14c1047f-366` 对应的日志数据。在该时间段内的关键错误信息中，出现了多种显著的问题模式，我将对其进行全面扫描和分析。\n\n根据日志内容，这些异常包含以下关键词：\n- `context canceled`\n- `failed to convert currency`\n- `Maximum call stack size exceeded`\n- `Error while dialing`\n- `connection refused`\n- `could not load plugin`\n\n同时，这些错误主要集中于两个服务：\n1. **Frontend**\n2. **CurrencyService**\n\n接下来，我将分析日志中的错误模式并找出显著的调用链异常。\n以下是根据日志分析的显著异常调用链及其可能原因：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"context canceled\",\n    \"failed to convert currency\",\n    \"Maximum call stack size exceeded\",\n    \"Error while dialing\",\n    \"connection refused\",\n    \"could not load plugin\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple instances logged errors related to 'Maximum call stack size exceeded' during currency conversion requests, suggesting an issue in the recursive or iterative logic in the service.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log message: \\\"conversion request failed: RangeError: Maximum call stack size exceeded\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend experienced 'context canceled' errors frequently when calling the currencyservice for conversion of product prices and shipping costs.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log message: \\\"failed to convert currency: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend reported 'connection refused' when establishing a transport connection to currencyservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log message: \\\"connection error: transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.39.78:7000: connect: connection refused\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Failed to load required OpenTelemetry plugins for monitoring, which might affect reporting or trace tracking.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Log message: 'could not load plugin @opentelemetry/plugin-http of module http'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 总结\n- **根本原因推测**:\n  - CurrencyService 可能存在代码或逻辑问题，导致递归调用耗尽资源（Maximum call stack size）。\n  - Frontend 在调用 CurrencyService 时多次发生传输层问题（连接拒绝）或者调用被取消。\n  - Observability (监控工具) 的插件加载失败可能加剧问题排查难度。\n\n建议对 CurrencyService 作进一步的性能测试，同时分析 Frontend 和服务间通讯异常以明确网络或配置问题。"}
