ing**\n  - 影响 CheckoutService 向 CurrencyService 的后续调用\n\n#### **拓扑关系中的异常传播**\n分析调用链上下游的波及影响：\n\n1. **Frontend -> Checkout**\n   - CheckouteService 的异常延迟显著 (1014008765ms)\n   - CheckoutService 同时传播 Context Cancel 或 Connection Error 到 CurrencyService\n\n2. **CurrencyService -> Backend**\n   - CurrencyService 的错误触发 `Connection Refused` 和 `Context Canceled`\n\n3. **RecommendationService -> ProductCatalog**\n   - **推荐服务**调用与 **产品目录**的延迟虽有异常但权重较小 (倍数未超过 2)\n\n---\n\n### 初步结论与假设\n根据上述异常链的扫描数据：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"checkoutservice->currencyservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"context_canceled\",\n    \"transport_closing\",\n    \"connection_refused\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"CurrencyService 调用扩展 Connection Refused 和 Context Cancel 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Context \\\"canceled\\\" 的错误频发于呼叫 currency 的链路。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Checkout 调用受 Currency 超慢响应延迟影响。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CurrencyService 的正常/异常耗时差距较大，超过正常耗时的 6464 倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Front-End 调用因上下游传播造成高延迟\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend 和下一个直接依赖链路的各服务耗时依次异常递增\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "14c1047f-366", "component": "currencyservice", "reason": "logic issues caused 'Maximum call stack size exceeded' and connection errors", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LogSearch(currencyservice)", "observation": "Observed 'Maximum call stack size exceeded' errors in logs."}, {"step": 2, "action": "TraceAnalysis(14c1047f-366)", "observation": "Latency spike traced to CurrencyService calls."}, {"step": 3, "action": "LoadMetrics(currencyservice)", "observation": "Identified significant delay multiplier of up to 6.57x."}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
